headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Test Track
content:
LS Car Meet members can always traipse over to the Test Track and give the Annis ZR350, Karin Calico GTF, and Pfister Comet S2 a spin around the columns, free of charge.

Head to the LS Car Meet icon on your GTA Online map to gain access to the Test Track. Use the interaction menu to invite other players to join you on the Test Track.
